## Why This Is Asked
Tests advanced GPU orchestration on Kubernetes, including MIG-aware allocation, cross-namespace fairness, and interaction with device plugins.

## Key Concepts
- MIG-based GPU allocation and fragmentation handling
- CRD design with per-namespace quotas
- Reconciliation loop with safe preemption decisions
- NVIDIA device plugin integration
- Observability: metrics, events, and alerts

## Code Example
```javascript
// Pseudo reconcile loop for GpuPoolPolicy
async function reconcile(policy) {
  const current = await fetchAllocations(policy);
  const desired = computeMigAlloc(policy, current);
  await applyAllocations(desired);
  updateStatus(policy, { allocatedGpus: sum(desired), conditions: "Healthy" });
}
```

